{"tid":2234210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果： 今年4月誤將尼泊爾漢當成確診患者送院  懷疑入院時錯食藥物 結果出院兩星期後離奇死亡","createTime":"2020-10-07T16:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T01:30:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"76c5a50086ee210ca63713cafaee806fec2a034d","tid":2234210,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"衞生署今年4月自爆「擺烏龍」誤將尼泊爾漢當成確診患者送院，一天後始發現出錯。事主太太向《蘋果》控訴，丈夫出院後因頭痛等再送院，結果一去不返，約2星期後宣告不治。家屬質疑事主留院時被當成確診者治療，質疑曾誤服藥物，他離院後肝功能異常亦無人跟進，至今死因未明，促當局盡快交代，還丈夫一個公道。《蘋果》查詢後醫管局即約見家屬，稱病人生前無服食治療肺炎藥物，初步證實患罕見遺傳病，個案已交死因庭處理。<br />\n<br />\nJane稱他們因同住人士確診武漢肺炎而須入住駿洋邨接受檢疫，並無病徵，4月6日丈夫和22歲兒子獲通知確診，丈夫先送往聯合醫院，兒子因床位不足延後送院，並非如當局指將2人檢測報告調亂。翌日她收到當局來電指丈夫原來並非確診，她追問為何出錯，對方只稱「really sorry」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/CWF7D746UJAHDLBR42CML6VH4U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GjJ-Ed7q6n75oBnuqZNDlYqBNe5FFL6u_yog-O9VGJgfcHjMmfbn0vUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FCWF7D746UJAHDLBR42CML6VH4U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2GjJ-Ed7q6n75oBnuqZNDlYqBNe5FFL6u_yog-O9VGJgfcHjMmfbn0vUw&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5MWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=4cce62c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FCWF7D746UJAHDLBR42CML6VH4U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2GjJ-Ed7q6n75oBnuqZNDlYqBNe5FFL6u_yog-O9VGJgfcHjMmfbn0vUw&h=794ba6e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/CWF7D746UJAHDLBR42CML6VH4U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GjJ-Ed7q6n75oBnuqZNDlYqBNe5FFL6u_y